"use strict";(self.webpackChunkdocs=self.webpackChunkdocs||[]).push([[63297],{77424:(e,i,t)=>{t.r(i),t.d(i,{data:()=>l});const l={key:"v-28b1b590",path:"/C#/Web/%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91.html",title:"",lang:"zh-CN",frontmatter:{},excerpt:"",headers:[{level:3,title:"1.地址重定向",slug:"_1-地址重定向",children:[]}],git:{updatedTime:1655779244e3,contributors:[{name:"panzhiyue",email:"30484534+panzhiyue@users.noreply.github.com",commits:1}]},filePathRelative:"C#/Web/地址重定向.md"}},93860:(e,i,t)=>{t.r(i),t.d(i,{default:()=>r});const l=(0,t(57293).uE)('<h3 id="_1-地址重定向" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_1-地址重定向" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 1.地址重定向</h3><p>简介:用Intelligencia.UrlRewriter实现URL重写</p><h4 id="_1-下载intelligencia-urlrewriter-dll文件" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_1-下载intelligencia-urlrewriter-dll文件" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 1.下载Intelligencia.UrlRewriter.dll文件</h4><h4 id="_2-将intelligencia-urlrewriter-dll引用到你的website程序中" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-将intelligencia-urlrewriter-dll引用到你的website程序中" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 2.将Intelligencia.UrlRewriter.dll引用到你的website程序中</h4><p><img src="http://localhost:4000/images/pasted-48.png" alt="玖涯博客"></p><h4 id="_3-配置webconfig" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-配置webconfig" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 3.配置webconfig</h4><ol><li>添加　Configuration section handler:</li></ol><div class="language-xml ext-xml line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-xml"><code>&lt;configSections&gt;\n  &lt;section\n   name=&quot;rewriter&quot;\n   requirePermission=&quot;false&quot;\n   type=&quot;Intelligencia.UrlRewriter.Configuration.RewriterConfigurationSectionHandler, Intelligencia.UrlRewriter&quot; /&gt;\n &lt;/configSections&gt;\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ol start="2"><li>添加 UrlRewriter mapper HttpModule:</li></ol><div class="language-xml ext-xml line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-xml"><code>&lt;system.web&gt;\n  &lt;httpModules&gt;\n   &lt;add\n    type=&quot;Intelligencia.UrlRewriter.RewriterHttpModule, Intelligencia.UrlRewriter&quot;\n    name=&quot;UrlRewriter&quot; /&gt;\n  &lt;/httpModules&gt;\n &lt;/system.web&gt;\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ol start="3"><li>添加 重写规则到 web.config的configuration结点中，如下</li></ol><div class="language-xml ext-xml line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-xml"><code>&lt;rewriter&gt;\n&lt;rewrite url=&quot;/tags/(.+)&quot; to=&quot;/tagcloud.aspx?tag=$1&quot; /&gt; \n &lt;/rewriter&gt;\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ol start="4"><li>整个web.config文件</li></ol><div class="language-xml ext-xml line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-xml"><code>&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot;?&gt;\n &lt;configuration&gt;\n     &lt;configSections&gt;\n         &lt;section\n             name=&quot;rewriter&quot;\n             requirePermission=&quot;false&quot;\n             type=&quot;Intelligencia.UrlRewriter.Configuration.RewriterConfigurationSectionHandler, Intelligencia.UrlRewriter&quot; /&gt;\n     &lt;/configSections&gt;\n     &lt;appSettings/&gt;\n    &lt;connectionStrings/&gt;\n    &lt;system.web&gt;\n        &lt;httpModules&gt;\n            &lt;add\n                type=&quot;Intelligencia.UrlRewriter.RewriterHttpModule, Intelligencia.UrlRewriter&quot;\n                name=&quot;UrlRewriter&quot; /&gt;\n        &lt;/httpModules&gt;\n\n    \n        &lt;compilation debug=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;\n        \n        &lt;authentication mode=&quot;Windows&quot;/&gt;\n\n    &lt;/system.web&gt;\n    \n    &lt;rewriter&gt;        \n        &lt;rewrite url=&quot;~/tags/(.+)&quot; to=&quot;~/tag/tagcloud.aspx?tag=$1&quot; /&gt;\n        &lt;rewrite url=&quot;~/video&quot; to=&quot;~/Class/Default.aspx&quot; /&gt;\n        &lt;rewrite url=&quot;~/class/(.+)&quot; to=&quot;~/Class/Default.aspx?classid=$1&quot; /&gt;\n\n        &lt;rewrite url=&quot;~/test_([a-zA-Z]+).aspx$&quot; to=&quot;~/Show.aspx?Code=$1&quot; processing=&quot;stop&quot; /&gt;\n        &lt;rewrite url=&quot;~/test_([a-zA-Z]+).html$&quot; to=&quot;~/Show.aspx?Code=$1&quot; processing=&quot;stop&quot; /&gt;\n    &lt;/rewriter&gt;\n    \n&lt;/configuration&gt;\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ol start="5"><li>如果需要重写为htm、其它扩展名或者没有扩展名的url时，需要在IIS中设置</li></ol><p>设置方法如下： 在windowXP系统中：</p><p>１） Open Up IIS and Navigate to the “Home Directory Tab” ２）Select “Configuration” ３）Click “Add” and enter “C:\\WINDOWS[Microsoft.NET](http://microsoft.net/)\\Framework\\v2.0.50727\\aspnet_isapi.dll” in the Executable box. For the file extension, enter “.*”. Finally, make sure that “Check that file exists” is not checked. 在window 2003server中请参考： http://urlrewriter.net/index.php/support/installation/windows-server-2003/</p>',17),n={},r=(0,t(63243).Z)(n,[["render",function(e,i){return l}]])},63243:(e,i)=>{i.Z=(e,i)=>{const t=e.__vccOpts||e;for(const[e,l]of i)t[e]=l;return t}}}]);